<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #d4d3e2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #252725, #2092f0); /* Gradient background */
            color: #fff; /* Text color */
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card button {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card button:hover {
            background-color: #d4d3e2;;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333; /* Footer background color */
            color: #fff; /* Text color */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%-include('partials/nav.ejs')%>
    <header style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; color: #333;">
        <h1>Welcome to Predictor</h1>
        <h2>Ebike & Cycle Count Prediction</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Live Location</h2>
            <p>Stay updated with real-time tracking of e-bikes and cycle stations near you. Our live location feature provides accurate information on available bikes, stations, and routes, ensuring a seamless riding experience.</p>
            <button id="exploreBtn">Explore</button> <!-- Added id attribute -->
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Language</h2>
            <p>Enjoy our platform in your preferred language. Our language feature offers multilingual support, allowing you to navigate through the application with ease. Choose from a variety of languages to personalize your experience.</p>
            <button>Select Language</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2>E-bike Count</h2>
            <p>Track the availability of e-bikes in your area with our e-bike count feature. Whether you're planning a commute or leisure ride, our platform provides real-time updates on e-bike availability, ensuring you never miss out on a ride.</p>
            <button>Check Availability</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Predictor App. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Add event listener to the "Explore" button
        document.getElementById('exploreBtn').addEventListener('click', function() {
            // Redirect to the location.ejs page
            window.location.href = '/auth-session-main/views/location.ejs';
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
